column1: Table S3: Constraints implemented to simulate the Average European (AE) diet supplemented with taurocholate, glycocholate, taurochenodeoxycholate, and glycochenodeoxycholate. In each community model, the dietary, luminal, and fecal exchange and transport reactions shared by all joined microbes were constrained.
